&lt;P&gt;Cyber Claw: &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Cyber Claw&#39;s eyes went wide. No Primal? How was that possible? What did she miss? &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&quot;What? Primal is no longer here?&quot; she snarled. She bared her teeth at Striker. &quot;You thought I should have known that?&quot; Her voice tipped a little, but she picked it back up. &quot;I have been &lt;EM&gt;missing&lt;/EM&gt; in action for sometime.&quot; Oh, she hoped Carnage was right about Dinobot. &quot;But I have returned! Now, who is in charge?&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt;From: Yanshosh@... &lt;BR&gt;&gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@egroups.com &lt;BR&gt;&gt;To: nbwrpg@egroups.com &lt;BR&gt;&gt;Subject: Re: Neo Beast Wars &lt;BR&gt;&gt;Date: Sat, 3 Jun 2000 22:10:33 EDT &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;::Prowl/Striker:: &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;One of Prowl&#39;s eyebrows raises as Iron Raptor leaves him in charge and tells &lt;BR&gt;&gt;him to put up the scans. She was good at giving orders, but he wasn&#39;t under &lt;BR&gt;&gt;her command, Striker was his commander. &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;He shruggs. He&#39;d tell her later. He turns to bring up the scans as her &lt;BR&gt;&gt;transmission reaches his comm-link. He turns and looks at Striker, realizing &lt;BR&gt;&gt;it was too late to stop him. &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;He swears under his breath, turning to face Sniper. &quot;Yeah, go ahead,&quot; he &lt;BR&gt;&gt;says. &lt;BR&gt;&gt;~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ &lt;BR&gt;&gt;Striker frowns at Cyber Claws responce. &quot;Primal is not on the planet,&quot; he &lt;BR&gt;&gt;says, you should know that, you&#39;ve been here for quite a while....&quot; &lt;BR&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;Get Your Private, Free E-mail from MSN Hotmail at &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.hotmail.com/&quot;&gt;http://www.hotmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/html&gt;
